0:22:34.160,0:22:38.260
Out! Go!

0:22:38.260,0:22:40.840
Send them out.

0:22:40.840,0:22:44.020
Give them a red card. Send him out.

0:22:44.020,0:22:45.880
You have no business with him.

0:22:45.880,0:22:53.780
When you send him out of the way, there is no way -  you can score.

0:22:53.780,0:22:59.440
But today, many of us, what we do, we give satan just a yellow card.

0:22:59.440,0:23:03.560
"I will give you another chance, satan. I will give you a warning. Let's try again."

0:23:03.560,0:23:10.140
You give him a yellow card, instead of you to take your position in the believer's authority,

0:23:10.140,0:23:15.720
'You satan, you have no business in my life, my family, my marriage, my career. Get out!"

