0:23:37.080,0:23:44.040
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:23:44.040,0:23:54.280
No mortal man or devil can supersede the plan of God for your life.

0:23:54.280,0:24:08.020
There is only one person who can get you out of the will of God -  and that is you.

0:24:08.020,0:24:10.540
That is you.

0:24:10.540,0:24:14.640
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:24:14.640,0:24:21.060
One of the greatest gifts God has given us is the freedom to make decisions.

0:24:21.060,0:24:24.520
All of us who have fallen made a decision

0:24:24.520,0:24:31.900
and all of us who have not fallen faced a similar temptation and made a different decision.

0:24:31.900,0:24:36.100
It is not our challenges, temptations, troubles that make us fall;

0:24:36.100,0:24:39.180
it is our reaction to them.

0:24:39.180,0:24:43.100
While some of us yield to the pressure and make wrong decisions,

0:24:43.100,0:24:46.880
others face the same pressure and make the right decisions.

0:24:46.880,0:24:56.380
Whoever you yield yourself to obey, that is whose servant you are.

0:24:56.380,0:25:00.320
Romans 6:16.

0:25:00.320,0:25:07.300
Brethren, our heart is a treasury.

0:25:07.300,0:25:16.620
Luke 6:45 says that a good man brings forth good things out of the good that is stored up in his heart

0:25:16.620,0:25:24.800
but an evil man brings forth evil things out of the evil stored up in his heart.

0:25:24.800,0:25:28.960
What are you storing up in your heart?

0:25:28.960,0:25:36.780
Pride or humility?
Love or hatred?

0:25:36.780,0:25:41.480
Offence or forgiveness?

0:25:41.480,0:25:47.320
What you store up in your heart will be revealed at the point of temptation.

0:25:47.320,0:25:50.280
Temptation provokes what you are hiding, what you are storing.

0:25:50.280,0:25:54.240
What you have been keeping in your heart provokes that temptation.

0:25:54.240,0:25:58.340
That your weakness comes out in the face of temptation.

0:25:58.340,0:26:00.880
What you have been keeping, hiding, harbouring in your heart.

0:26:00.880,0:26:04.400
Look at Judas Iscariot in the Bible - the betrayer.

0:26:04.400,0:26:07.120
Judas Iscariot  lived and walked with Jesus

0:26:07.120,0:26:12.380
He was one of the twelve that Jesus sent out to heal the sick and deliver the demon-possessed.

0:26:12.380,0:26:17.060
He heard the teachings, he saw the miracles, he lived with Jesus.

0:26:17.060,0:26:25.300
But the Bible says in John 12:4-6 that Judas Iscariot harboured the secret sin of stealing.

0:26:25.300,0:26:30.240
He took from the money bag when no one was looking.

0:26:30.240,0:26:35.400
What he harboured in his heart gave satan a foothold to enter

0:26:35.400,0:26:41.000
and manipulate him to the point of betraying the Son of God.

0:26:41.000,0:26:43.920
Cain - you know the story of Cain and Abel in the Bible.

0:26:43.920,0:26:47.920
Let's quickly turn there; turn to the Book of Genesis.

0:26:47.920,0:26:54.200
Genesis 4:7.

0:26:54.200,0:26:58.960
You know, Cain gave an unworthy offering -

0:26:58.960,0:27:02.220
an offering to honour himself and dishonour God.

0:27:02.220,0:27:06.260
God was not happy; God told him in that Genesis 4:7,

0:27:06.260,0:27:09.380
"If you do what is right, will you not be accepted?

0:27:09.380,0:27:21.740
But if you do not do what is right, sin is crouching at your door;

0:27:21.740,0:27:26.100
it desires to have you but you must rule over it."

0:27:26.100,0:27:32.440
Even with this warning from God, because Cain bore a grudge against his brother Abel,

0:27:32.440,0:27:35.780
because God accepted Abel's offering,

0:27:35.780,0:27:44.540
satan had a foothold in his heart and manipulated him to the point of murdering his own brother.

0:27:44.540,0:27:48.020
On the contrary, Joseph - we know the story of Joseph.

0:27:48.020,0:27:54.060
Do you know the reason why Joseph did not succumb to the temptation from Potiphar's wife?

0:27:54.060,0:27:58.960
Potiphar's wife was trying to seduce Joseph, wanted to sleep with him at all cost.

0:27:58.960,0:28:04.200
Do you know the reason why Joseph did not give in or yield or submit to that temptation?

0:28:04.200,0:28:11.720
He knew who he was; he was a child with a promise of God.

0:28:11.720,0:28:16.840
I tell you today - you are children of promise.

0:28:16.840,0:28:19.680
You are children of destiny.

0:28:19.680,0:28:23.080
You are children with a promise from God.

0:28:23.080,0:28:31.100
Your destiny does not permit you to give your heart to fleshly desires.

0:28:31.100,0:28:40.000
Your destiny, your promise from God is too precious to be corrupted, tainted, perverted.

0:28:40.000,0:28:42.660
Your destiny does not permit you.

0:28:42.660,0:28:45.120
Consider your destiny.

0:28:45.120,0:28:59.180
Your destiny does not allow you to waste time on things that have no lasting value and significance.

0:28:59.180,0:29:06.220
Your destiny does not permit you to strive and struggle against flesh and blood.

0:29:06.220,0:29:10.300
Consider your destiny.

0:29:10.300,0:29:12.740
Be God conscious.

0:29:12.740,0:29:15.780
Cultivate a consciousness of God.

0:29:15.780,0:29:19.920
If you are conscious of God, your heart will not rest until it rests in Him.

0:29:19.920,0:29:23.880
You go where Jesus will not be welcomed -

0:29:23.880,0:29:27.600
your spirit will be agitated until you leave that place.

0:29:27.600,0:29:31.860
You have a conversation with someone and you sense a satanic influence - you will quickly cut it off.

0:29:31.860,0:29:39.260
But today, the problem is that satan's traps for us are often hidden.

0:29:39.260,0:29:45.060
He would disguise himself as an angel of light and come with his hidden agenda.

0:29:45.060,0:29:49.880
It takes the grace, the strength of one grounded in the Word of God,

0:29:49.880,0:29:56.560
to be able to identify the devil's tricks for what they are.

0:29:56.560,0:29:59.380
If you ask any man here, "Will you sleep with a snake?",

0:29:59.380,0:30:02.180
he will say, "No, over my dead body!"

0:30:02.180,0:30:07.980
Satan knows that so he will put a spirit of snake inside a beautiful lady.

0:30:07.980,0:30:13.520
By the time you meet them, it's not just your bodies that meet; it's your spirits.

0:30:13.520,0:30:18.480
No physical protection can withstand spiritual contamination.

0:30:18.480,0:30:25.460
Many destinies have been diverted, many homes broken, many lives shattered

0:30:25.460,0:30:28.480
because we've given our hearts away to fleshly desires.

0:30:28.480,0:30:32.600
I'm coming to a conclusion, brethren, but I want to tell you something that happened to me;

0:30:32.600,0:30:37.440
how God used Prophet T.B. Joshua to preserve my life.

0:30:37.440,0:30:42.640
When I came here to The SCOAN as a visitor, many many years ago;

0:30:42.640,0:30:46.200
I was in the prayer line, I was about 14-15 years old.

0:30:46.200,0:30:50.320
Prophet T.B. Joshua walked up to me and gave me a word of prophecy.

0:30:50.320,0:30:58.580
