0:30:58.580,0:31:03.820
and you have to be very careful because she is demon-possessed".

0:31:03.820,0:31:06.940
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:31:06.940,0:31:08.460
I didn't do that on the outside.

0:31:08.460,0:31:11.480
You know when you receive a prophecy, you say, "Yes, Man of God, it's true".

0:31:11.480,0:31:18.080
But within me, I was like, "Ah! What? There is a lady close to me that is possessed?"

0:31:18.080,0:31:22.860
In fact, I began to think, "Maybe it is this one. Oh my God, what is happening?"

0:31:22.860,0:31:25.400
You should have seen me when I got back to UK.

0:31:25.400,0:31:30.920
If a lady came close to me, "Be gone from me, you satan!"

0:31:30.920,0:31:35.900
I quickly gave her the red card because I was so scared that someone would come.

0:31:35.900,0:31:39.620
This is Prophet T.B. Joshua who had told me; I didn't know who the person was.

0:31:39.620,0:31:49.040
But that prophecy preserved me from making a stupid mistake.

0:31:49.040,0:31:52.080
As a young man, you know the temptations that we face -

0:31:52.080,0:31:55.100
peer pressure, temptations up and down, here and there.

0:31:55.100,0:31:59.660
Anytime this temptation would come, I would remember what the Prophet had told me,

0:31:59.660,0:32:03.420
"There is a lady that is close to you. She is demon-possessed".

0:32:03.420,0:32:07.580
"Ay! Ok, I’m gone! Goodbye. Thank you."

0:32:07.580,0:32:11.720
Leave the place just like Joseph. Get out.

0:32:11.720,0:32:15.560
When Joseph was tempted, he didn't just stay there; he got out.

0:32:15.560,0:32:23.300
Tell your neighbour, "Get out before sin gets in".

0:32:23.300,0:32:38.000
If you ask Samson, he will tell you -  a night of pleasure is not worth a lifetime of blindness.

0:32:38.000,0:32:40.400
In conclusion, brethren:

0:32:40.400,0:32:47.140
The truth of this sermon is enough to change your life.

0:32:47.140,0:32:54.860
But don't just listen to this sermon; study the sermon of your own life.

0:32:54.860,0:33:00.980
Your life experience will testify to this truth.

0:33:00.980,0:33:06.040
Poison is poison, irrespective of how it is packaged.

0:33:06.040,0:33:11.100
Please, don't tempt the devil to tempt you.

0:33:11.100,0:33:14.240
Life already has enough challenges.

0:33:14.240,0:33:17.500
You are a Christian; you have declared war against satan.

0:33:17.500,0:33:21.840
There are already enough challenges in life for you to create one for yourself -

0:33:21.840,0:33:28.620
to create your own trouble, challenge, temptation.

0:33:28.620,0:33:32.940
Jesus said to His disciples, "I pray your faith will not fail".

0:33:32.940,0:33:37.100
It means He knew situations would come that would test them, tempt them

0:33:37.100,0:33:39.000
and try to remove them from their faith

0:33:39.000,0:33:43.540
but He said, "I pray your faith will not fail".

0:33:43.540,0:33:48.320
This means, our faith may fail but not fall off.

0:33:48.320,0:33:56.380
If faith is kept up in the hour of temptation, though we are cast down, we will not be utterly destroyed.

0:33:56.380,0:34:04.600
And if God allows it, it will not lead to our end, to our downfall.

0:34:04.600,0:34:07.220
It will lead to our promotion.

0:34:07.220,0:34:12.740
Just stay in line with the will of God.

0:34:12.740,0:34:17.680
And He is there to see you through whatever life brings.

0:34:17.680,0:34:26.460
May God bless His Word in the midst of our hearts, in Jesus' name.

